title: Convert Flac Files to Mp3 With Best Quality (Vbr) in a Directory
tags: @zettel _method mp3 ffmpeg flac
roam-id: 864a89be-11ef-416b-a96f-fa01b04afd6b
type: text/markdown

zsh/bash version

    for file in *.flac; do ffmpeg -i "$file" -q:a 0 "${file%.flac}.mp3"; done

fish version

``` fish
for file in *.flac
    ffmpeg -i "$file" -q:a 0 "$(string replace -r '\.flac$' '.mp3' -- $file)"
end
```
